### Ascend API — Accountability / Commitments
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api/v1
@token = REPLACE_WITH_JWT

### Create a new commitment
POST {{baseUrl}}/accountability/commitments
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "No social media for 7 days",
  "description": "I commit to staying off all social media platforms this week",
  "dueAt": "2025-07-01T23:59:59Z",
  "xpStake": 50
}

###

### Get my commitments (all statuses)
GET {{baseUrl}}/accountability/commitments?page=1&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Get only PENDING commitments
GET {{baseUrl}}/accountability/commitments?status=PENDING
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Mark commitment as completed
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/accountability/commitments/COMMITMENT_UUID/complete
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Mark commitment as failed
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/accountability/commitments/COMMITMENT_UUID/fail
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "failureNote": "Slipped up on day 3 — will try again next week"
}
